;\">纺织品、服装与奢侈品</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">1.6</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">安踏体育</span><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">(02020)</span></td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">93.1（-1.9%）</td></tr><tr><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">煤炭</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">1.3</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">中国神华</span><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">(01088)</span></td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">34.75（1.8%）</td></tr><tr><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">运输</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">0.8</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">港铁公司</span><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">(00066)</span></td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">27.95（0.4%）</td></tr></table></div>",
